0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34570,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/11\/29\/hudhayfah-fitnah-worst\/","url_meta":{"origin":36600,"position":1},"title":"Hudhayfah on Fitnah: Worst tribulation to not know good or evil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 29, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Amir reported: Hudhayfah, may Allah be pleased with him, was asked, \u201cWhich trial is the worst?\u201d Hudhayfah said, \u201cIt is when good and evil are before you and you do not know which of them to follow.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 37569 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064f\u0626\u0650\u0644\u064e \u062d\u064f\u0630\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38379,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/24\/refuge-many-fitnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36600,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet seeks refuge from many evil trials","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 24, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from the trials and punishment of the Hellfire, from the trials and punishment of the grave, from the evil of the trials of wealth, and from the evil of the trials\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32862,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/22\/when-fitnah-out-of-control\/","url_meta":{"origin":36600,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: If trials get out of control, take care of yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: We were gathered around the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while he mentioned tribulations, saying, \u201cIf you see that people have disordered their commitments, diminished their trusts, and are as jumbled as this,\u201d and he interlaced his fingers. I stood to come\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17969,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/31\/fitnah-absorbed-in-desires\/","url_meta":{"origin":36600,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: Trials will immerse hearts of people in desires","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 31, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTribulation will be exposed to the hearts of people like a reed mat woven, stick by stick. Any heart afflicted by them will have a black mark put into it, but any heart that rejects them will\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6126,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/09\/fitnah-refuse-unjust-wars\/","url_meta":{"origin":36600,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: Success in refusing to fight unjust wars","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWoe to the Arabs from an evil approaching! He has succeeded who restrains his hand from fighting.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4249 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0648\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644\u064c \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0628\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/36600","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"